{"tid":503450,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【阿信屋賣樓】3個月沽17物業套1.27億 林偉駿：賣樓非減債","createTime":"2017-12-19T00:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T06:30:01.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6a276cf1b91e56a80020aa4185f7db0e6d293f0d","tid":503450,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T00:43:38.000Z","msg":"【新增影片】<br />\n<br />\n759阿信屋母公司CEC國際（759）過去3個月內沽出14個住宅單位、兩個舖位及一個工廈單位，共17物業，共套現1.27億元。<br />\n阿信屋老闆林偉駿接受傳媒訪問時表示，套現非為減債：「我不是專業樓市投資者，現在樓價已處極高水平，所以陸續出售收租單位，對從事實業公司來說，是合理決定。」<br />\n根據土地註冊處資料顯示，阿信屋透過子公司高雅線圈，出售6伙得寶花園、4伙淘大花園及4伙嘉和園單位，共套現6,261萬元，較2005年至2010年買入總價2,181.8萬元，賬面共賺4,079萬元，升值190%。<br />\n當中賺得最多的，是2006年斥資115萬買入的淘大D座低層3室，實用面積375方呎，於10月以495萬賣出，賺380萬元。<br />\n目前阿信屋仍持有4伙得寶花園以及6伙淘大花園。<br />\n另外，阿信屋於9月亦以5,200萬元出售觀塘成運大廈工廈，持貨3年賺920萬。同時，亦以578萬及705萬，沽出屯門啟豐商場地下4號及1樓5號舖，後者目前由阿信屋自行租用。據了解，阿信屋仍持有4個商舖或工廈單位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171218/57596335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171218%2F57596335&d=OOlVbkzSc%2FpoKpTIQIzIf26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=82bc978c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171218%2F57596335&h=2e3159d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171218/57596335</a>"},{"pid":"76671ca43c4d55a74f0e6bdd03b33d555e743112","tid":503450,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T00:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 曾經風光過 過大海輸下錢"},{"pid":"c3531b814530189f73d614f013fe3d3e24bc77c5","tid":503450,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T00:46:42.000Z","msg":"抵死 賣咁多大陸野"},{"pid":"1a4bd45fe9a83657569dab46fa5bee1078c94809","tid":503450,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T00:48:25.000Z","msg":"入去只買濕紙巾"},{"pid":"0ecb6c8e325d0c48e3c65ab4344b4a81473f706f","tid":503450,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T00:48:53.000Z","msg":"炒樓仲好賺"},{"pid":"13c426d5dd75f1ec68d2e41bbdba001364ecca12","tid":503450,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T01:26:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入去只買濕紙巾</blockquote><br />\n日版一丁都ok"},{"pid":"0ceac04880225ff107d58876455d1a5c41539644","tid":503450,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"剛剛星期日66折買114咖啡$16.x<br />\n同買薯片"},{"pid":"b018015dcd837457f7bbf13f374ac60ff437255a","tid":503450,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:22:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入去只買濕紙巾</blockquote><br />\n日版一丁都ok</blockquote><br />\n日版可樂都ok"},{"pid":"4ffd5c313dc2352a50d92611f9ec0b9a7bdcf628","tid":503450,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"759近兩年其實要蝕錢"},{"pid":"b4c667b239e39f28cd1b5c73a5e00f4c0149cf2c","tid":503450,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T06:30:01.000Z","msg":"收到風？"}]}